---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import "../styles/conditions.scss";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <div class='circle-red-top'></div>
  <div class='circle-green-top-left'></div>
  <div class='circle-blue-mid-left'></div>
  <div class='circle-green-bot-left'></div>
  <div class='circle-red-bot-right'></div>
  <div class='circle-green-mid-right'></div>

  <div class='text-contract'>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>
      Welcome to FlavorShare! Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy
      Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and share your information
      when you use our app. By using FlavorShare, you agree to the practices
      described in this policy.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>
      We collect the following types of information when you use FlavorShare:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email, phone number, and date
        of birth.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Future Data:</strong> We plan to collect payment information, location
        data, and health-related information in upcoming updates.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>All data is collected via direct user input.</p>

    <hr />

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use the information we collect for the following purposes:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Personalization:</strong> To tailor the appâ€™s features to your preferences.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Account Management:</strong> To create and manage your account.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Future Use:</strong> We may introduce analytics, performance tracking,
        and marketing communications in future app versions, allowing the app to
        stay free for people who wish to.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>We may also use your data to comply with legal obligations.</p>

    <hr />

    <h2>3. Sharing Your Information</h2>
    <p>
      We do not currently share your personal data with any third parties.
      However, we use third-party services to operate the app:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>OAuth:</strong> For identification via Apple, Google, and Instagram.
      </li>
      <li><strong>Firebase:</strong> For user management.</li>
      <li><strong>DigitalOcean:</strong> For data storage.</li>
      <li><strong>Render:</strong> For server hosting.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      These services are bound by their own privacy policies, which we encourage
      you to review.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h2>4. User Control</h2>
    <p>You have control over your personal data. Specifically, you can:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Delete Your Account:</strong> Permanently remove your account and
        associated data via the app.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Contact Us:</strong> Reach out via in-app email support in the Help
        section for any data-related concerns.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <hr />

    <h2>5. Data Storage & Security</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Storage:</strong> User data is stored on cloud servers managed by
        DigitalOcean and locally on your device.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Retention:</strong> Data is retained until you delete your account.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Security Measures:</strong> Data encryption is handled by Firebase
        and DigitalOcean-managed MongoDB.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <hr />

    <h2>6. Compliance with Privacy Laws</h2>
    <p>
      We strive to comply with applicable privacy laws, including those in North
      America. As the app evolves, we will ensure compliance with regulations
      such as:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR):</strong> For users in
        the European Union.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA):</strong> For users in California.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      FlavorShare is designed for users aged 13 and above. We do not knowingly
      collect data from children under 13.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      If you have any questions, concerns, or requests related to this Privacy
      Policy, please get in touch with us at: <a
        href='mailto:benjamin.lefebvre.1024@gmail.com'
        >benjamin.lefebvre.1024@gmail.com</a
      >
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h2>Updates to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We encourage you to
      review it periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your
      data. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <p>Thank you for using FlavorShare!</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
